data.description: Do not miss out on this great opportunity/home in the up-and coming town of Hayden. The main level features 1,400 square feet with three bedrooms and two bathrooms.Nicely upgraded with new LVP flooring, trim , and new GE stainless steel appliances. Opportunity awaits downstairs, which is partially finished, 1,400 additional square feet, and framed out for two bedrooms, bath, and an additional living space. Plumbing and electrical have been installed and fully permitted, with an opportunity for the new owner to pick out their own finishes, fixtures, flooring, etc. and gain some great equity. This home sits in an excellent location within the neighborhood, and is located  on a corner lot with fenced in yard. Large two car garage and driveway for all of your toys. Come make 338 Honeysuckle Drive your new home today!
